        intro: "Read the clinic letter excerpt below, then answer the questions about it.",
        letter: "Dear Dr Owusu,\n\nRe: Mrs Patricia Hale, DOB 22/09/1961\n\nThank you for referring this patient who presents with right knee pain. X-rays demonstrate bone on bone OA of the medial compartment. She has failed physiotherapy and NSAIDs. I have discussed conservative options versus proceeding to arthroplasty, and she would like to proceed to a right TKR. I have arranged pre-assessment and will see her for post-operative review at 6 weeks.\n\nYours sincerely,\nMiss R. Bennett, Consultant Orthopaedic Surgeon",
