        title: "Exercise 1: Interpret a gastroenterology clinic letter",
        type: "letter-interpretation",
        intro: "Read the clinic letter excerpt below, then answer the questions about it.",
        letter: "Dear Dr Cross,\n\nRe: Mrs Diane Foster, DOB 06/09/1969\n\nThank you for referring this patient who presents with altered bowel habit and PR bleeding. Colonoscopy demonstrated a sigmoid polyp, which was removed. Biopsies were taken and histology is awaited. I have arranged follow-up once results are available, and would advise surveillance colonoscopy depending on the findings.\n\nYours sincerely,\nMr J. Whitmore, Consultant Gastroenterologist",
